title: [P3D] Prepar3D v3 Professional Plus 3.3.5.17625
description:
Hi everyone, just uploading the full install for P3D v3.3.5 for convenience. 

I'm uploading it because i found that when you just update the client from 3.0 to 

3.3.5 you have a problem with some addons that use inbuilt P3D default windows e.g. 

ProATC, Active sky next (the legit version :) ) and so on. You also must uninstall 

and then install the content for 3.3.5.


Of course it contains cracked API.dll and SDK if someone is interested. 




It not my work, just uploading it to share. 

Chears Dace
